message.body: Hey! Hunter and I are gonna ride bikes to chamounix mansion and look for mushrooms in a bit if you wanna come?!
Is it cool if we all come? I imagine Eliana won't last super long anyway, but no problem if you'd rather it was adults-only.
How soon do you think you'll leave?
It will be super fun! You Guys wanna meet at our place when you are ready?
I've just gotta change but we are ready when you guys are.
Cool. We'll get a move on. I'm guessing 25 minutes, if that's cool.
That's perfect! See you soon. I'm excited you guys can come!
